<topic id="document-type-classpath-tab">
  <title>Classpath Tab</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Document type configuration dialog box<indexterm>Classpath
          tab</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_oyn_bgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Classpath</uicontrol> tab displays a list of folders and
        <xref keyref="glossentry_jar"><term>JAR</term></xref> libraries that hold implementations
      for API extensions, implementations for custom <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode operations,
      various resources (such as stylesheets), and <xref keyref="glossentry_framework"
          ><term>framework</term></xref> translation files. <ph keyref="product"/> loads the
      resources looking in the folders in the order they appear in the list (from top to
      bottom).</p>
    <p id="p_pyn_bgk_54b">To open the <uicontrol>Classpath</uicontrol> tab of the <uicontrol>Document type</uicontrol>
      configuration dialog box, <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/>, go to
        <uicontrol>Document Type Association</uicontrol>, use the <xref
        href="preferences-document-type-association.dita#preferences-document-type-association"
          ><uicontrol>New</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol>,
        <uicontrol>Duplicate</uicontrol>, or <uicontrol>Extend</uicontrol> button</xref>, and click
      on the <uicontrol>Classpath</uicontrol> tab.</p>
    <p id="p_qyn_bgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Classpath</uicontrol> tab includes the following actions:<dl id="dl_ryn_bgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_syn_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Add16.png" placement="inline"/>New</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens a dialog box that allows you to add a resource to the table in the
              <uicontrol>Classpath</uicontrol> tab. <ph
              conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/specify-path-ph"/><note
              conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/note-wildcards-in-path" id="note_tyn_bgk_54b"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_uyn_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Wrench16.png" id="image_l2t_4ns_tr"
            />Edit</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens a dialog box that allows you to edit a resource in the
              <uicontrol>Classpath</uicontrol> tab. <ph
              conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/specify-path-ph"/><note
              conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/note-wildcards-in-path" id="note_vyn_bgk_54b"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_wyn_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" placement="inline"
              />Delete</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Deletes the currently selected resource from the list.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_xyn_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/MoveUpEntry16.gif" id="image_fpb_rr1_5r"/>Move
              Up</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Moves the selected resource up one spot in the list.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_yyn_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/MoveDownEntry16.gif" id="image_xht_qr1_5r"/>Move
              Down</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Moves the selected resource down one spot in the list.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry product="author developer editor" id="dlentry_zyn_bgk_54b">
          <dt><xref
              href="share-classloader-between-framework-and-plugin.dita#share-classloader-between-framework-and-plugin"
                ><uicontrol>Use parent classloader from plugin with ID</uicontrol></xref></dt>
          <dd>Use this option to specify the ID of a <xref keyref="glossentry_plugin"
                ><term>plugin</term></xref>. The current <term>framework</term> has access to the
            classes loaded for the <term>plugin</term>.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
